dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents municipalities for Oneida County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Oneida_Municipalities_2014.gdb.
uw_supplemental_s: This metadata was updated to reflect that the data is no longer restricted and has been opened for public use.Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit: https://gis.co.oneida.wi.us/oneview/
